I MISSED YOUR PHONE CALL--

36:31.360 --> 36:34.284
- HAVE A SEAT, JULIA.

36:35.840 --> 36:38.809
[clears throat]

36:38.920 --> 36:40.535
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

36:40.640 --> 36:41.629
- I WAS
AT MY SON'S BASEBALL GAME.

36:41.750 --> 36:43.809
I'M SORRY.
MY PHONE WAS IN MY PURSE--

36:43.920 --> 36:45.433
- NOT THIS MORNING.

36:45.540 --> 36:48.191
THE LAST SIX MONTHS, JULIA.

36:48.300 --> 36:50.609
- UM, IF THIS IS
ABOUT THE REQUEST

36:50.720 --> 36:52.859
FOR ADMISSIONS, I SPOKE
TO OPPOSING COUNCIL, AND--

36:52.960 --> 36:54.348
- IT DIDN'T WORK.

36:54.450 --> 36:56.236
THEY FILED A MOTION TO DEEM,

36:56.350 --> 36:58.932
AND THE COURT'S
GONNA GRANT IT.

36:59.040 --> 37:01.486
IT'S OVER.

37:01.590 --> 37:03.410
JULIA, WHAT THE HELL
HAPPENED TO YOU?

37:03.530 --> 37:04.622
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?
YOUR HOURS HAVE BEEN DISMAL,

37:04.730 --> 37:09.076
AND NOW YOU
MISS A DISCOVERY DEADLINE?

37:09.190 --> 37:11.522
- LEON, I'M SORRY.
I-I WILL MAKE THIS UP.

37:11.640 --> 37:13.915
- DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHAT THIS IS COSTING THIS FIRM?

37:14.020 --> 37:15.533
CLIENT'S THREATENING
TO WALK.

37:15.640 --> 37:17.699
THIS IS A MULTI-MILLION-DOLLAR
SCREW-UP.

37:17.820 --> 37:20.880
TWO YEARS AGO,
THIS WOULDN'T HAVE HAPPENED.

37:20.990 --> 37:23.367
A YEAR AGO,
THIS WOULDN'T HAVE HAPPENED.

37:23.480 --> 37:24.026
THIS IS ROOKIE CRAP.
- YOU'RE RIGHT.

37:24.130 --> 37:27.588
I-I-I APOLOGIZE.

37:27.690 --> 37:29.373
- WHAT WE'RE TRYING
TO SAY, JULIA,

37:29.480 --> 37:34.417
IS YOU WERE
ON A PARTNER TRACK.

37:35.660 --> 37:37.457
- I WAS?

37:37.560 --> 37:40.108
- YOU NEED
TO TELL US RIGHT NOW

37:40.220 --> 37:42.313
THAT THIS
WILL NEVER HAPPEN AGAIN,

37:42.430 --> 37:44.398
AND YOU NEED TO TELL US
THAT YOU WANT THIS JOB,

37:44.500 --> 37:47.424
THAT YOUR FOCUS IS 100%
ON YOUR CLIENTS.

37:53.130 --> 37:55.883
JULIA.

37:58.060 --> 38:01.780
- I DON'T THINK
THAT IT IS.

38:01.900 --> 38:06.030
I-I DON'T THINK
THAT I AM 100% COMMITTED.

38:06.140 --> 38:07.892
- JULIA.

38:08.000 --> 38:11.140
- I THOUGHT THAT I
COULD DO IT ALL, BUT I CAN'T.

38:11.250 --> 38:15.619
NOT NOW, ANYWAY.

38:20.430 --> 38:22.113
THANK YOU

38:22.230 --> 38:26.940
FOR THESE LAST NINE YEARS,
LEON.

38:27.060 --> 38:28.812
I QUIT.

38:37.000 --> 38:39.230
- SO RIGHT NOW,
YOUR BATTING AVERAGE IS 100%,

38:39.350 --> 38:41.796
