BUT IT'S A LOT BETTER

38:46.080 --> 38:47.866
THAN MINE STILL
'CAUSE MY BATTING AVERAGE

38:47.980 --> 38:52.110
LIFETIME WAS .147,
BUT NOW I'M RETIRED.

38:52.220 --> 38:54.780
- SWEET.
- MM-HMM.

38:54.880 --> 38:55.733
- SO, UH, MAYBE WE
COULD HAVE, LIKE, A GAME

38:55.850 --> 38:58.978
OF CATCH ONE DAY.
- YEAH, WHY NOT?

38:59.090 --> 39:01.536
- IT'D BE PRETTY COOL.

39:02.610 --> 39:03.884
- WHAT DO YOU THINK?

39:03.990 --> 39:04.888
- YOU CAN FEEL FREE
TO MIX AND MATCH, YOU KNOW.

39:04.990 --> 39:07.618
WE LIKE THOSE KIND
OF WACKY POTIONS.

39:07.720 --> 39:09.335
- OKAY.

39:09.450 --> 39:10.894
- I'M GOIN' STRAIGHT ORANGE
ON THIS, THOUGH.

39:11.000 --> 39:13.230
- ALL RIGHT,
SO I'M GONNA TAKE THE FALL

39:13.350 --> 39:15.727
FOR THE CONCOCTION, OKAY.
- YES. EXACTLY.

39:15.830 --> 39:17.058
- SO WHAT DO YOU DO,
AMBER?

39:17.180 --> 39:20.035
- UH, WELL, MY UNCLES
OWN A RECORDING STUDIO

39:20.150 --> 39:21.139
IN THE HAIGHT,
SO I WORK THERE.

39:21.250 --> 39:23.798
- COOL.

39:23.910 --> 39:27.732
- SO YOU WERE
IN AFGHANISTAN, RIGHT?

39:27.840 --> 39:29.899
- YEAH.

39:31.290 --> 39:34.509
I'M BACK.

39:34.610 --> 39:36.987
- WELCOME BACK.
- THANKS.

39:37.090 --> 39:39.604
- READY?
- YEAH, YEAH.

39:40.510 --> 39:42.614
- LET'S MOVE IN TOGETHER.

39:45.270 --> 39:48.376
- REALLY?
- YEAH.

39:48.480 --> 39:51.552
- WELL, WHAT ABOUT,
UM, THE PLAN,

39:51.660 --> 39:53.480
WAITING FOR DREW
TO GRADUATE, AND--

39:53.590 --> 39:55.831
- WHY--YOU KNOW,
WHY WAIT?

39:55.940 --> 39:58.215
LET'S DO THIS THING.
- LET'S DO THIS THING.

39:58.320 --> 39:59.241
ALL RIGHT, YEAH.
- YOU THINK?

39:59.360 --> 40:01.146
- YEAH?
- I LIKE THAT IDEA A LOT.

40:01.260 --> 40:02.636
- GOOD.

40:02.740 --> 40:04.776
- AS I WALK
ABOVE THE PAVEMENT

40:04.880 --> 40:07.326
I CAN FEEL YOU
WALKING WITH ME

40:07.430 --> 40:09.398
CARRYING ME

40:09.510 --> 40:12.570
- UH, YOU CAN.
THERE'S NO LAW, I GUESS.

40:12.680 --> 40:15.331
- AND I HEAR
ABOVE THE SILENCE

40:15.440 --> 40:16.850
ALL THESE VOICES

40:16.960 --> 40:23.069
SCREAMING LOUDLY
AT MY EAR

40:23.170 --> 40:27.766
SHED THEIR FEAR

40:27.870 --> 40:29.519
- I TOLD YOU.
[laughter]

40:29.630 --> 40:33.452
- DADA.
DADA. DADA.

40:33.560 --> 40:38.429
- SHED THEIR FEAR

40:38.530 --> 40:44.605
ON ME

40:44.710 --> 40:47.406
- LOOK WHO'S HERE.

40:47.510 --> 40:48.716
- OH, MY GOD!
- HI.

40:48.820 --> 40:51.436
- AMONGST THE HOLY SITES

40:51.550 --> 40:54.405
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

40:54.520 --> 40:56.750
DID ANY OF YOU GUYS
KNOW SHE WAS COMING?

40:56.860 --> 40:59.556
- GRANT ME STRENGTH
