OF YOU.

41:08.560 --> 41:09.527
- AH, IT'S SO GOOD
TO SEE YOU.

41:09.630 --> 41:12.110
- DID YOU KNOW?
- NO.

41:12.220 --> 41:14.154
NO, I DIDN'T KNOW.

41:18.570 --> 41:21.949
- HEY, UM, HONEY,
CAN YOU TAKE THE KIDS

41:22.060 --> 41:23.857
