41:23.960 --> 41:25.439
- UM, HEY, YOU WANNA GO
TO THE ARCADE?

41:25.550 --> 41:27.643
COME ON, IT'LL BE FUN.
COME ON, GUYS.

41:27.760 --> 41:29.261
LET'S ARCADE IT UP.
LET'S GO PLAY SOME GAMES.

41:33.140 --> 41:34.721
ARCADE.

41:42.290 --> 41:43.871
- I LOVE YOU ALL
SO MUCH.

41:43.980 --> 41:47.848
I JUST WANNA SAY THAT,
UM--

41:47.950 --> 41:50.839
AND THERE'S SOMETHING
THAT I NEED TO TELL YOU.

41:53.440 --> 41:54.361
[exhales]

41:54.470 --> 42:00.784
- OOH

42:04.340 --> 42:10.825
OOH

42:13.490 --> 42:17.312
AS I WALK
ABOVE THE PAVEMENT

42:17.430 --> 42:18.806
I CAN FEEL YOU

42:18.910 --> 42:22.494
WALKING WITH ME,
CARRYING ME

42:24.050 --> 42:28.123
AND I HEAR
ABOVE THE SILENCE

42:28.230 --> 42:31.097
